In [50]:
def plot_desicion_boundary(X, y, model, ax,title = ""):
    # fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(12, 8))
    ax.scatter(X[:, 0], X[:, 1], c=y, cmap="coolwarm")
    if not title:
        title = "Decision Boundary"
    ax.set_title(title)

    x_min, x_max = X[:, 0].min() - 0.1, X[:, 0].max() + 0.1
    y_min, y_max = X[:, 1].min() - 0.1, X[:, 1].max() + 0.1
    xx, yy = np.meshgrid(np.linspace(x_min, x_max, 100), np.linspace(y_min, y_max, 100))
    Z = model.predict(np.c_[xx.ravel(), yy.ravel()])
    Z = Z.reshape(xx.shape)
    ax.contourf(xx, yy, Z, cmap="coolwarm", alpha=0.2)
    # plt.show()

In [53]:
Cs = [0.001, 0.01, 0.1, 0.5, 1, 10, 100, 1000]
cols = 4
rows = 2
all = cols*rows
fig, axes = plt.subplots(ncols=cols, nrows=rows, figsize=(20,10))
axes = axes.flatten()
for i in range(all):
    title = f"$C={Cs[i]}$"
    lr = LogisticRegression(penalty="l2", C=Cs[i])
    lr.fit(X, y)
    plot_desicion_boundary(X, y, lr, ax=axes[i], title = title)
In [55]:
Cs = [0.001, 0.01, 0.1, 0.5, 1, 10, 100, 1000]
cols = 4
rows = 2
all = cols*rows
fig, axes = plt.subplots(ncols=cols, nrows=rows, figsize=(20,10))
axes = axes.flatten()
for i in range(all):
    title = f"$C={Cs[i]}$"
    lr = LogisticRegression(penalty="l1", C=Cs[i], solver="saga")
    lr.fit(X, y)
    plot_desicion_boundary(X, y, lr, ax=axes[i], title = title)

degrees = [1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8]
cols = 4
rows = 2
all = cols*rows
fig, axes = plt.subplots(ncols=cols, nrows=rows, figsize=(20,10))
axes = axes.flatten()
for i in range(all):
    title = f"$degree={degrees[i]}$"
    svc = SVC(degree=degrees[i], kernel="poly")
    svc.fit(X, y)
    plot_desicion_boundary(X, y, svc, ax=axes[i], title = title)
